# PowerEdge R720 (gen 12, 2U dual-socket).
#
# UNTESTED — gen 12 (iDRAC7) BMC firmware varied across the line;
# behavior between gen 11 (literal PWM) and gen 13 (clamps to safety)
# is unpredictable per-chassis. Default MIN_FAN=20 is conservative.
#
# Probe before lowering: send `ipmitool raw 0x30 0x30 0x02 0xff 0x05`
# from inside the container, watch RPM. If RPM drops to 0 (stall) or
# the BMC raises lcr alarm, stay at 20. If RPM clamps to a safe high
# value (BMC is protecting you), 10 is fine.

: "${MIN_FAN:=20}"
